OL,3,CStars pay tribute to Titanic and The
OL,4,CLord of the Rings actor Bernard Hill
OL,6,FITV News Reporter Anila Dhami looks
OL,7,Fback at the life and career of Bernard
OL,8,FHill
OL,10,FActor Bernard Hill, best known for his
OL,11,Froles in Titanic and The Lord of the
OL,12,FRings trilogy, has died aged 79, his
OL,13,Fagent confirmed.
OL,15,FHill's agent, Lou Coulson, told the PA
OL,16,Fnews agency that he died in the early
OL,17,Fhours of Sunday.
