OL,3,CStars pay tribute to Titanic and The
OL,4,CLord of the Rings actor Bernard Hill
OL,6,FThe actor played Captain Edward Smith
OL,7,Fin the Oscar-winning 1997 epic romance
OL,8,FTitanic, which starred Leonardo
OL,9,FDiCaprio and Kate Winslet.
OL,11,FDominic Monaghan has said his Lord Of
OL,12,FThe Rings co-star Bernard Hill has
OL,13,F"passed to the grey havens", as he
OL,14,Fpaid tribute to the actor.
OL,16,FHe also portrayed Theoden, King of
OL,17,FRohan, in The Lord Of The Rings
OL,18,Ftrilogy directed by Sir Peter Jackson.
