OL,3,CStars pay tribute to Titanic and The
OL,4,CLord of the Rings actor Bernard Hill
OL,6,FHill joined the Lord Of The Rings cast
OL,7,Ffor the second film in the trilogy,
OL,8,F2002's The Two Towers, which won two
OL,9,FAcademy Awards for best sound editing
OL,10,Fand best visual effects.
OL,12,FHe returned to the franchise for
OL,13,F2003's The Return Of The King, which
OL,14,Fpicked up 11 Oscars, including best
OL,15,Fpicture and best director for Sir
OL,16,FPeter.
OL,18,FHill also starred in drama series Boys
OL,19,FFrom The Blackstuff, and the 2015 BBC
OL,20,Fadaptation of Hilary Mantel's novel
OL,21,FWolf Hall.
