OL,6,FThe BBC described him as an
OL,7,F"incredible talent" who "blazed a
OL,8,Ftrail across the screen" during his
OL,9,Fcareer.
OL,11,FActress and musician Barbara Dickson,
OL,12,Fwho starred with him in a musical
OL,13,Fbased on the Beatles, was among those
OL,14,Fpaying tribute, describing him as a
OL,15,F"marvellous actor".
OL,17,FAlongside a photo of them together,
OL,18,Fshe wrote: "It's with great sadness
OL,19,Fthat I note the death of Bernard Hill.
